def test_package_name_is_package_object(self):
        import tests

        pkg = tests
        path = 'test_asset.py'
        package_name, filename = self._callFUT(path, pkg)
        self.assertEqual(package_name, 'tests')
        self.assertEqual(filename, 'test_asset.py')
